Invocation Name: ethergem headquarters
des:
With the EtherGem Headquarters skill, you can use Alexa to get various market information about the EtherGem cryptocurrency, as well as a description of the project.

Commands Alexa can respond to are:

- Get Price
- Get Market Cap
- Get Total Supply
- More Information
- Help

There are plans to make more features available in the future, such as roadmap updates and checking on quarry node balances.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
